title: Crunk Music 101 Ft. Big Sam | Ep. 103
itunes:title: Crunk Music 101 Ft. Big Sam | Ep. 103
description:
Big Sam 1/3 of the Eastsideboyz (Formally Lil John and the EastsideBoyz) stopped by to shed some light on how his run with Lil John all got started and how it came to an end. Big Sam aka Gas Can Shawty breaks down how Atlanta's Crunk music scene took over the world and he also hops on some funk freestyles with Karlous and Ronnie! Karlous Miller and Ronnie Jordan hold it down on another educational hip hop episode of The 85SouthShow!
